    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of use. While the exterior paint still holds a great shine, you might find a few tiny stone chips upon close inspection, typical for a car of this age. Overall, it\u2019s a reliable and attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
